@ENDNODE
@NODE 0301 "Citazioni"

@{b}Worf:@{ub} What is my ranking position?
@{b}Troi:@{ub} You're commander, and First Officer.
@{b}Worf:@{ub} Are we still married?
@{b}Troi:@{ub} Yes.

@{b}Wesley:@{ub}   Captain,  we  are  receiving  two  hundred  and  eighty-five
thousand hails.

@{b}Worf (al replicatore):@{ub} Champagne.
@ENDNODE
@NODE 0302 "Citazioni"

@{b}Q:@{ub}   Goodbye  Jean  Luc, I'm gonna miss you, you had such a pontential, but
then again, all good things must come to an end.

@{b}Q:@{ub}  That is the exploration that awaits you, not mapping stars and studying
nebula, but charting the unknown possibilities of existence.
@ENDNODE
@NODE 0303 "Citazioni"

@{b}Picard:@{ub}  and sky's the limit.

@{b}Q:@{ub}  May whatever God you believe in have mercy on your soul

@{b}Data:@{ub}   Captain,  another  ship  is  decloacking, bearing two one five mark
three one o, it's the Enterprise
@ENDNODE
